                        <h2>6. Server Locations</h2>
                        <p>We store and process your information on servers located in Unite States, Canada and Germany data centers.</p>
                        <p>Hosting providers we use:
                            <br /> Hetzner Online GmbH, Industriestr. 25 91710 Gunzenhausen, Germany
